<hymn_number>11049</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- slạm yswd ḥyạty .. wlạ yʿtryh ạlạ̉fwl
 rjạʾ yṭmỷn qlby .. wlyuⁿ frḥ lạ yzwl
 nʿym yʿm kyạny .. ạ̉nạ fy ạlmsyḥ
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉nạ fyh sẖkẖṣ jdyduⁿ .. ạ̉nạ fyh qlbuⁿ sʿyd
 wạ̉ʿml mhmạ yryd .. wly fyh mhmạ ạ̉ryd
 (ạ̉nạ fy ạlmsyḥ)2
 2- wḥbh ymlạ̉ qlby .. ldẖạk ạ̉ḥb ạljmyʿ
 wạ̉ʿks nwr kẖlạṣy .. wbsẖry ạlfdạʾ ạ̉dẖyʿ
 wạ̉ḥyạ ạ̉mynạ lạ̉ny .. ạ̉nạ fy ạlmsyḥ
 3- yqynaⁿạ wbʿd ạkẖtbạry .. msyry wrạʾ ạlḥbyb
 ạ̹lyh stbqy ḥyạty .. ffyh ḥyạty tṭyb
 wyḥlw nsẖydy lạ̉ny .. ạ̉nạ fy ạlmsyḥ</lyrics>
<title>slạm yswd ḥyạty</title>
</song>